<section id='Raise'>
<title>Raise</title>

<!--command-->
<cmdsynopsis>
    <command>Raise</command>
</cmdsynopsis>
<!--/command-->

<para>Allows the user to raise a window. Note that this raises a window
only in its layer. To bring a window to the absolute top, use</para>

<programlisting>
<fvwmref cmd="AddToFunc"/> raise-to-top
 + I <fvwmref cmd="Layer"/> 0 ontop
 + I Raise
</programlisting>

<para>where ontop is the highest layer used in your setup.</para>

</section>
